sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as Caller / Orchestrator
    participant Oracle as Oracle Contract
    participant Trace as ExecutionTraceLog
    participant Bridge as Oracle Bridge
    participant MCP as MCP Server

    Caller->>Oracle: requestReview(traceId, agentId, payloadHash)
    activate Oracle
    Note over Oracle: Validate authorization<br/>(onlyRegisteredOracle modifier)
    Oracle->>Trace: recordHop(traceId, agentId, actionName)
    Oracle-->>Bridge: emit ReviewRequested event
    deactivate Oracle

    activate Bridge
    Note over Bridge: ethers.js event subscription<br/>catches on-chain event
    Bridge->>MCP: POST tools/call (JSON-RPC 2.0)
    activate MCP
    Note over MCP: Execute tool handler<br/>(LLM inference / business logic)
    MCP-->>Bridge: Structured result
    deactivate MCP

    Note over Bridge: Sign TX with agent wallet<br/>(VaultSigner / HSM)
    Bridge->>Oracle: fulfillReview(traceId, agentId, resultHash, outcomeCode)
    deactivate Bridge

    activate Oracle
    Note over Oracle: Validate fulfillment<br/>(wallet + oracle binding check)
    Oracle->>Trace: recordHop(traceId, agentId, "fulfill")
    Oracle-->>Caller: emit ReviewCompleted event
    deactivate Oracle
